{"tid":1512272,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【白宮聯署】大陸AI辨識公司想香港上市，仲唔做野？","createTime":"2019-08-27T22:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T05:02:35.000Z","uid":215892,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2352737f1bde20280fcab1c09a811894620ad545","tid":1512272,"uid":215892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T22:24:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2PrRSLw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PrRSLw&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=845d5910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2PrRSLw</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">內地人臉識別技術公司曠視科技申上市 <br />\n或成第三隻同股不同權新股</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3202220/org/f438710fe1ab5e083aaf5aef2be08595.jpg/DyBr_2txuBNG7ytF7fd4ocnBI7ixfa68SOM_3EjjP9w?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3202220%2Forg%2Ff438710fe1ab5e083aaf5aef2be08595.jpg%2FDyBr_2txuBNG7ytF7fd4ocnBI7ixfa68SOM_3EjjP9w%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=8349dbc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府早前在<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">觀塘區率先引入智能燈柱，引起公眾關注對個人私隱問題</span></strong>。阿里巴巴有份投資的內地人臉識別技術公司曠視科技，昨日（25日）提交上市申請，公司去年虧損達33.51億元（人民幣‧下同），按年擴大3.4倍。公司將採同股不同權架構，為本港繼小米（1810）及美團（3690）後第三隻同股不同權股份。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>業務遍及106個內地城市</strong><br />\n根據申請文件，曠視主營業務包括個人物聯網、城市物聯網及供應鏈物聯網的解決方案。公司引述研究報告指，按去年收入計算，曠視為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國最大的聚焦於人工智能的城市物聯網解決方案提供商，為106個內地城市及企業客戶提供解決方案。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n截至今年6月底，曠視科技<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">上半年虧損擴大5.48倍至52億元</span></strong>，其中51.21億元為金融負債公允價值變動。撇除相關影響，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公司經營虧損為1.15億元，按年擴大12.2%</span></strong>，其中收入增長3.55倍至14.27億元；撇除管理層認為不能反映經營表現項目的影響，公司上半年按年轉虧為盈，錄得3,270萬元經調整淨利潤。<br />\n============================<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">蝕到仆街都可以黎香港上市搵真錢，知唔知點解？？？</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母因爲有 Goldman Sachs, Citi, JP Morgan做保薦人阿！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔想比佢好過？</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">拿拿聲同我簽左佢！！記得Share叫人簽！！！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/investigate-restrict-us-companies-support-communist-chinas-high-tech-mass-surveillance-terrorism-acts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Finvestigate-restrict-us-companies-support-communist-chinas-high-tech-mass-surveillance-terrorism-acts&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=6765f5c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/investigate-restrict-us-companies-support-communist-chinas-high-tech-mass-surveillance-terrorism-acts</a>"},{"pid":"1e0a1a8642109393ee0ba7589df0625e1b116e0c","tid":1512272,"uid":281342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T22:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ePPTkox.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FePPTkox.jpg&h=753ead90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G9Cd4Qd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG9Cd4Qd.png&h=7bdb5fbc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/upXBiad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FupXBiad.jpg&h=079e8db4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6b79Daf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6b79Daf.jpg&h=915ee5dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c216601472ef41b2593f5fbee6538f25269dce33","tid":1512272,"uid":215892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T22:27:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff303e8006afe8adda90522a535af4e96e4e6076","tid":1512272,"uid":215892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T22:44:4